description: Quest-driven RPG Quest-driven Roguelike fantasy dungeon crawler RPG with a powerful story. Uncover the truths about your home village and the disappearance of your brother. Battle fierce monsters, gain experience and levels. Solve quests, find hidden treasures and improve your equipment. Please note that this is a work in progress, which means that all maps are not yet done. This is mainly a version for bug-hunting and compatibility testing. Please give feedback on the project page. Some of the content and graphics are released under non-free licenses: see GitHub page.
